scenes.description: Opening introduction featuring stylized visuals and background music.
Ninomae Ina'nis enters her 3D room and greets the audience.
Ina performs a 'Kabedon' (wall pin) for the audience as promised.
Ina expresses her excitement and explains the relay order for the 3D showcases.
Ina begins a tour of her 3D studio, starting with her art workspace.
